dc_description_s: This data layer represents block boundaries (for local redistricting) in Wisconsin in 2021.[This data has been collected as part of the 2021 local redistricting process in the State of Wisconsin. Data was submitted to the Legislative Technology Services Bureau through the WISE-LR (Wisconsin Shape Editor for Local Redistricting) application between August 2021 and February 2022. For specific information related to the local redistricting process, please visit: https://legis.wisconsin.gov/ltsb/local-redistricting/]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most current version of this dataset, please visit: https://gis-ltsb.hub.arcgis.com/
